type: scenario
name: kaijo/ssh-connection-flood-pfsense
description: >
  Detects SSH connection floods on pfSense systems, where attackers overwhelm
  the SSH service with rapid connection attempts. Optimized for pfSense CE/Plus
  FreeBSD/OpenSSH log formats.

author: kaijo
license: MIT
version: 0.1.6

labels:
  service: sshd
  platform: pfSense
  attack_type: flood
  vector: connection

tags:
  - pfSense
  - SSH
  - Security
  - Flood
  - FreeBSD

events:
  - connection_attempt
